image here is a patient, a patient who has cancer. So we start with that. And I'm very fortunate to

00:00:23.040 --> 00:00:29.280
be a small part of a team at Johnson & Johnson that works in a called cell therapy platforms.

00:00:29.280 --> 00:00:32.480
